docs.lead_paragraph: Despite earlier estimates that new exemptions to China's one-child policy would add up to 2 million extra births per year, only 700,000 newly qualified couples applied to have a second child this year, a Chinese official said.

headline.main: No Baby Boom From Easing of China's 1-Child Policy
